        <sponsor name-id="S370">Mr. Booker</sponsor> (for himself and <cosponsor name-id="S352">Mr. Heller</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSVA00">Committee on Veterans' Affairs</committee-name>
